FBIS3-11665 "drlat057_c_94005" FBIS-LAT-94-057 Document Type:Daily Report 24 Mar 1994 MEXICO Colosio Shot, Killed in Attack During Tijuana Campaign Stop Colosio's Death Confirmed PA2403050194 Mexico City XEW Television Network in Spanish 0438 GMT 24 Mar 94 PA2403050194 Mexico City XEW Television Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] The Presidency of the Republic has confirmed the death of Luis Donaldo Colosio, presidential candidate for the Institutional Revolutionary Party.
